---
title: Tex-Mex Corn Fritters & Sour Cream Slaw with Kumara Fries
description: These gloriously bright fritters are both crunchy and sweet, and are set off perfectly by an A-team of tangy sour cream slaw,
kumara fries and smokey aioli. If you fancy it, you could also break out your favourite hot sauce for these bad boys!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tex-mex-corn-fritters-sour-cream-slaw-e289b897.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/tex-mex-corn-fritters-sour-cream-slaw-60f8afe667189910264381ce-f574473d.pdf
